{
  "texts": [
    "This symbiosis will ultimately shape the trajectory for a reimagined grading paradigm that leverages the strengths of both educators and AI systems to foster a rich, equitable, and dynamic educational environment.",
    "LLMs signify a watershed moment for educational assessment, offering a forward-looking lens through which we might reimagine and reshape traditional grading into a model that befits the dynamism and demands of 21st-century learning.",
    "Our collective responsibility educators, technologists, policymakers, and students is to navigate this transition responsibly, ensuring that the future of grading with LLMs is as equitable and beneficial as innovative."
  ]
}